Title: Relates to the unauthorized practice of a profession, the unauthorized use of a professional title and the practice of esthetics
Summary: Relates to the unauthorized practice of a profession, the unauthorized use of a professional title and the practice of esthetics.
LawCode: Amd §§6512 & 6513, Ed L; amd §400, Gen Bus L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to the unauthorized practice of a profession and the unauthorized use of a professional title; and to amend the general business law, in relation to the practice of esthetics
